56:34.107 --> 56:42.449
Is pleasing Jehovah each day 
with the choices I make.


56:42.448 --> 56:47.586
He gave me all that I have; 
I’ll never forget it.


56:47.587 --> 56:51.925
I’m safe in his hands; 
I’ll never regret it.


56:51.925 --> 56:59.000
I’m building my future with him 
ev’ry step that I take.


57:00.867 --> 57:04.704
I’m building a future 
that never will end


57:04.703 --> 57:09.275
If I build it with help 
from Jehovah, my Friend.


57:09.275 --> 57:13.378
The happiest moments, 
