to take the message of this program


58:40.867 --> 58:43.570
—to build a future with Jehovah—


58:43.570 --> 58:45.572
to heart. 


58:45.572 --> 58:49.509
Prayerfully consider what you can do 


58:49.508 --> 58:52.678
to expand your ministry. 


58:52.678 --> 58:57.716
Always safeguard 
your most valuable possession


58:57.717 --> 59:02.422
—your precious relationship 
with Jehovah. 


59:02.422 --> 59:06.859
Never forget 
that there are more with you 


59:06.858 --> 59:09.628
than there are against you. 


59:09.628 --> 59:13.065
It is true that Satan, the demons, 


59:13.065 --> 59:16.068
and this world are against you. 


59:16.068 --> 59:18.838
But your brothers and sisters, 


59:18.838 --> 59:23.408
including the Governing Body, 
are with you; 


59:23.408 --> 59:27.280
the angels are with you; 


59:27.280 --> 59:33.085
the resurrected immortal anointed ones 
are with you; 


59:33.085 --> 59:35.588
Jesus is with you; 


59:35.588 --> 59:40.000
and most important, 
Jehovah is with you. 


59:41.193 --> 59:46.831
You are never alone!


59:46.832 --> 59:48.835
To conclude, 


59:48.835 --> 59:51.170
we have greetings 
to share with you 


59:51.170 --> 59:53.840
from the special convention 
that was held 


59:53.840 --> 59:56.608
in July of last year


59:56.608 --> 59:58.745
in Paris, France.


59:58.745 --> 1:00:01.547
I had the privilege 
of attending this convention 


1:00:01.547 --> 1:00:03.582
with Brother Kenneth Flodin,


1:00:03.582 --> 1:00:05.585
a helper to the Teaching Committee.


1:00:05.585 --> 1:00:09.588
While most of the convention program 
was in French, 


1:00:09.588 --> 1:00:11.890
it was simultaneously interpreted 


1:00:11.890 --> 1:00:15.127
into Croatian, English, 


1:00:15.127 --> 1:00:17.664
and Polish 
for the benefit 


1:00:17.663 --> 1:00:20.065
of the international delegates.


1:00:20.065 --> 1:00:22.068
You will be happy to know 


1:00:22.068 --> 1:00:24.436
that 71 new sisters 


1:00:24.437 --> 1:00:26.905
and 41 new brothers 


1:00:26.905 --> 1:00:31.000
symbolized their dedication 
through water baptism. 


1:00:32.645 --> 1:00:35.982
The oldest baptismal candidate 
was an 80-year-old sister 


1:00:35.982 --> 1:00:38.000
and the youngest 
was a 10-year-old.


1:00:39.385 --> 1:00:41.387
The young candidates 
had to overcome 


1:00:41.387 --> 1:00:44.390
various challenges in order 
to reach their goal 


1:00:44.390 --> 1:00:46.392
of baptism. 


1:00:46.392 --> 1:00:48.394
Four of them took this step 


1:00:48.393 --> 1:00:50.430
even though their parents 


1:00:50.430 --> 1:00:52.432
are not Jehovah’s Witnesses. 


1:00:52.432 --> 1:00:54.867
Many of these dear young ones 
had to overcome 


1:00:54.867 --> 1:00:56.869
peer pressure at school


1:00:56.868 --> 1:00:59.438
—pressure to do things 


1:00:59.438 --> 1:01:01.440
Jehovah does not like. 


1:01:01.440 --> 1:01:04.510
Two of the young brothers, 
also fleshly brothers, 


1:01:04.510 --> 1:01:07.613
used to play 
violent video games. 


1:01:07.613 --> 1:01:09.781
Through their personal Bible study 


1:01:09.782 --> 1:01:12.152
and the personal interest 
shown in them, 


1:01:12.152 --> 1:01:16.155
they came to understand 
Jehovah’s viewpoint on violence 


1:01:16.155 --> 1:01:20.860
and made the necessary changes 
to progress spiritually. 


1:01:20.860 --> 1:01:22.862
By taking this first step 


1:01:22.862 --> 1:01:26.199
of getting baptized, 
these brothers and sisters have shown


1:01:26.198 --> 1:01:29.568
that they want to build a future 


1:01:29.568 --> 1:01:31.603
with Jehovah. 


1:01:31.603 --> 1:01:33.171
Let us all do everything 


1:01:33.172 --> 1:01:37.410
we can to continue making 
spiritual progress, 


1:01:37.410 --> 1:01:42.782
which will bring 
Jehovah’s smile of approval. 


1:01:42.782 --> 1:01:48.487
Brothers and sisters, 
we love you very much. 


1:01:48.487 --> 1:01:51.690
This is JW Broadcasting 


1:01:51.690 --> 1:02:03.500
from the world headquarters 
of Jehovah’s Witnesses.

